channel.name: HEHKFABAYMW02 DICOM transformer
channel.description: This channels adds the DICOM tags: StationName, InstitutionName & InstitutionalDepartmentName to the DICOM images from Intego 2 (HEHKFABAYMW02)

step.name: Header
step.script: var mapping;try { mapping = tmp=msg; }catch (e) { logger.error(e); mapping = '';}channelMap.put('Header', validate( mapping , '', new Array()));

step.name: InstitutionName
step.script: var mapping;try { mapping = tmp['tag00080080']="HospitalName"; }catch (e) { logger.error(e); mapping = '';}channelMap.put('InstitutionName', validate( mapping , '', new Array()));

step.name: InstitutionNameLength
step.script: var mapping;try { mapping = tmp['tag00080080']['@len']=tmp['tag00080080'].toString().length; }catch (e) { logger.error(e); mapping = '';}channelMap.put('InstitutionNameLength', validate( mapping , '', new Array()));

step.name: DepartmentName
step.script: var mapping;try { mapping = tmp['tag00081040']="DepartmentName"; }catch (e) { logger.error(e); mapping = '';}channelMap.put('DepartmentName', validate( mapping , '', new Array()));

step.name: DepartmentNameLength
step.script: var mapping;try { mapping = tmp['tag00081040']['@len']=tmp['tag00081040'].toString().length; }catch (e) { logger.error(e); mapping = '';}channelMap.put('DepartmentNameLength', validate( mapping , '', new Array()));

step.name: StationName
step.script: var mapping;try { mapping = tmp['tag00081010']="HEHKFABAYW02"; }catch (e) { logger.error(e); mapping = '';}channelMap.put('StationName', validate( mapping , '', new Array()));

step.name: StationNameLength
step.script: var mapping;try { mapping = tmp['tag00081010']['@len']=tmp['tag00081010'].toString().length; }catch (e) { logger.error(e); mapping = '';}channelMap.put('StationNameLength', validate( mapping , '', new Array()));
